quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,71,Dni pojdem when my zvolat kazdy ludia dohromady ich rekord. Mat rad for those dat rekord righteousness they robit read ich zapisnica nie suffer maly injustice
  17,72,Mat rad for those je blind v this zivot they je blind Hereafter vecer a lot zly
  17,73,"They skoro diverted ona revelations my dat ona. They chudoba ona fabricate nieco inak, v poradie consider ona znamy"
  17,74,If nie bol my zosilnit ona ona skoro leaned them iba a maly kusok
  17,75,Had ona robit lenze my zdvojnasobit retribution ona v this zivot after smrt ona zalozit ziaden 1 pomoc ona us
  17,76,They skoro banished ona zem zrusit ona they revert ona lavy
  17,77,This bol consistently puzdro all posol my sent ona ona zalozit ze our system never zmenit